{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":550403,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"问题不在于工科生有没有人文素养吧，如果换个说法，可以要人文素养，也保留人文素养课程，但去掉这些人文方面的学院，你就认为这样没问题了吗？","timestamp":1605265719,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550407,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"🎣的罢","timestamp":1605265736,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550408,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"清华招人的时候又不知道他会这么想","timestamp":1605265738,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550418,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"上清华，分够就行，原dz虽然奇葩，也够格当清华学生","timestamp":1605265839,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550425,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"本身这些人文学科也是科学，而不是别的什么学科的附庸，也不是因为要提升理工科学生的人文素养而存在的，它们本来就是科学的一个分支，价值本身就是毋庸置疑的，用不着“提升理工科学生人文素养”来体现其价值。","timestamp":1605265916,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550448,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 课程是老师开的，没学院了老师去哪？","timestamp":1605266288,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550513,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 但显然不够格做一个清华人","timestamp":1605267343,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550532,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 赞同","timestamp":1605267631,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550619,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我觉得原dz不见得是多有优越感，好像是真心实意觉得文科没用（至少是对于理工学生没用）的，然而作为人文学生，感到最无奈的就是看到那个dz说文素课学了跟没学一样——某种程度上，文素课乃至于文科专业在大学里面被认为“水”确实是普遍现象——为什么会这样呢，唉","timestamp":1605268983,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550875,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":114783,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 为啥，贵清是你家的吗？各有各的想法，何必呢","timestamp":1605273481,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":4,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":114783,"reply":10,"tag":null,"text":"#114629\n为什么清华要招原dz这样一点人文素养都不想要的只想学技术的理工科生呢？他真的能写出语句通顺的足够发刊的中or英论文吗？建议把dz合并到蓝翔，多收几个愿意接受一定人文素养的理工科学生过来，而不是什么人都招，毕竟还是要尊重人才意愿因材施教。","timestamp":1605265462,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782643,"url":"","vote":{}}}